David, the move to on-device processing isn't just a legal shield; it is a massive scalability win. By shifting the biometric analysis from our backend GPU clusters to the user's TEE (Trusted Execution Environment), we effectively offload the most compute-intensive part of the 'Pulse' to the edge. 

